			<div class="content" id="post-content-2919506">
									

<p>Hey there kids! We've been having some talks amongst the Staff, and figured we'd get some input from the user base, see how you guys feels, so:</p>
<h1><span>Do you feel that there are rules on the site that are harsh, unnecessary, or have discouraged you from contributing?</span></h1>
<p>Please be open and honest with us. We here at the SCP site Staff care about your opinions, and we want to know what can be done better.</p>
<p>This is a poll/discussion thread, so feel free to interact with comment threads if you agree with or disagree with something. We just really want to hear from you!</p>

