			<div class="content" id="post-content-2964414">
									

<p><em>Hey-o</em>, still very much a newbie to this website (despite being here a few months), and I can honestly say the rules are fine by me. I read through them several times before and after I joined here, and everything seems relatively reasonable to me. If I were to have any issue I'd probably just read 'em again to see what's wrong, or ask an experienced user on here.</p>
<p>As for contribution, my only problem has been procrastination. I've been revising my first SCP article a lot after I had it critiqued on the Drafts and Critiques forum, and sometimes I've hit a writing block or have been distracted. Other than that, my experiences on this site so far have been pretty okay.</p>

