<p>I have a problem with SCPs that deal with NSFW content, like steely dan.</p>
<p>I think the site should be more uhh, &quot;Reproduction free&quot;. Stating how a creature reproduces is fine, but using objects used for sex as ideas, just sorta bothers me.</p>
<p><strong>EDIT!:</strong> What have I started&#8230;</p>
<p>The main thing is that I am not bothered by gore/violence (like some usual popular SCPs, like SCP-096 and SCP-173, for instance.) but I am sensitive to certain things. especially for me, because I am 20 and I have seen some crap. So much so that I don't like talking about it&#8230;</p>

